title: American Style Chicken Schnitzel Sando with Caramelised Onions, Burger Sauce and Fries
description: We've got a tasty selection of schnitzel in the menu inspired by global flavours perfectly paired with crispy chicken! This American Style Chicken Schnitzel Sando isn't your regular chicken sandwich as it's loaded with caramelised onions and lashings of burger sauce, served with fries on the side.
